tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"著衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"著衫我驚佢會熱 但都試下 thx"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:42:47.000Z","msg":"無需要著衫，著左佢都會唔鍾意<br />\n其實兔怕熱相對唔怕凍，不過你隻兔咁細個都留意下啦<br />\n<br />\n以下地方可以學多D野<br />\n香港兔友協會（入面有知識同好多兔等領養）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=f06e8815\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港FB gp（要答問題先入到）：<br />\n香港兔友群組<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/50297388704/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F50297388704%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=d66635ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/50297388704/</a><br />\nMINI-HOUSE 兔友會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/minihouse.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fminihouse.info%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=0831bfe5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/minihouse.info/</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣愛兔協會（知識專頁）<br />\n<a href=\"http://time.rabbit.org.tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.rabbit.org.tw%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=1ce24ef7\" target=\"_blank\">http://time.rabbit.org.tw/</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎加入養兔行列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我隻兔9歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />養兔比養貓多D野要留意，去上面D link了解多D野先，有咩問題一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1baa67fe2d7fdea50acb553c661a916d25aca167","tid":2332993,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"迷你暖風機  可唔可以?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.crabwarehouse.com/products/machino-mini-warmer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crabwarehouse.com%2Fproducts%2Fmachino-mini-warmer&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=6f7abe9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crabwarehouse.com/products/machino-mini-warmer</a>"},{"pid":"476301a293ce32436b086efe1a71d1a3b82609f9","tid":2332993,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">兔子是應該要被絕育...(寵物兔)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"70572db596441ef07529fcbd7f488929b326e152","tid":2332993,"uid":237355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"火爐,暖下佢"},{"pid":"50ece1932140d54fbd4942ea75e7d071a0198087","tid":2332993,"uid":167792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"佢會唔係唔熟新環境有d驚？<br />\n我記得兔仔唔係好怕凍<br />\n反而係怕熱..."},{"pid":"21cfc7be33b168b5f2ca43f2744d7e9dcbeffa0f","tid":2332993,"uid":181419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1baa67fe2d7fdea50acb553c661a916d25aca167","tid":2332993,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"迷你暖風機  可唔可以?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.crabwarehouse.com/products/machino-mini-warmer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crabwarehouse.com%2Fproducts%2Fmachino-mini-warmer&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=6f7abe9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crabwarehouse.com/products/machino-mini-warmer</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"唔需要對住佢吹架<br />\n如果屋企有大暖風機吹晒成個環境就ok<br />\n有人會買爬蟲用暖燈，買100w就得<br />\n<br />\n我兔籠喺窗邊<br />\n但都係真係好凍，10-12度先會開暖燈/暖風<br />\n無咁凍嘅話毛巾蓋籠都可以架啦<br />\n<br />\n不過樓主咁細隻兔，驚凍都可以試下<br />\n但一定唔好對住佢吹"},{"pid":"29e8063690ac65844bcce445b72ea6fc5668cb50","tid":2332993,"uid":181419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50ece1932140d54fbd4942ea75e7d071a0198087","tid":2332993,"uid":167792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"佢會唔係唔熟新環境有d驚？<br />\n我記得兔仔唔係好怕凍<br />\n反而係怕熱..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"對，兔怕熱多過怕凍<br />\n<br />\n夏天佢地好易熱親<br />\n要準備一盒盒嗰啲冰種<br />\n地下整塊雲石板/降溫板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a358fb5ace7189ccfaa1f6a4b1c9c88a4aa6538e","tid":2332993,"uid":250271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba971926f0fe22954a23ab33f90b23d02913896","tid":2332993,"uid":250271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5c1f929dccfe7fc0f078379d46ff25d04ccfca","tid":2332993,"uid":181419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a358fb5ace7189ccfaa1f6a4b1c9c88a4aa6538e","tid":2332993,"uid":250271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5r0TRv2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5r0TRv2.png&h=f8007f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿婆與幾粒冬至湯圓<br />\n <br />\nps你個籠貴嘢嚟wo"},{"pid":"