msg":"4粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁乖嘅佢廁所咁整齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個隻以前用啲細廁玩到癲，自從換左個巨廁之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />穩如泰山<br />\n<br />\nps個籠比個sales吹大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想訂造1個但一直搵唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T15:15:22.000Z","msg":"啱啱執完先係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有少少腳瘡，我拎走咗廁所鐵網<br />\n平時會掘到周圍都係紙，但識去廁所屙尿<br />\n<br />\n想搵咩籠？<br />\n如果唔介意無櫃桶，西人牌子啲籠好大個<br />\n我呢個都成米長，佢地仲有120以上，不過多數無轆<br />\n<br />\n你啲墊好好呀，阿婆舖呢隻瑜珈墊先無咁咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d0c44f7397fadddf037c10f934da3b87ac1d42","tid":2332993,"uid":15813,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T23:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8943b95321c18f9eea8f5dc39ca233ea680d3659","tid":2332993,"uid":109629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T23:05:13.000Z","msg":"攬住佢就可以幫佢保到暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917a578708d00b38664be5adaf6393ad67b88153","tid":2332993,"uid":345579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"比啲毛巾擺落紙箱<br />\n或者去買vet bed<br />\n利申養咗9 年佢都冇用過，最多係地氈訓"},{"pid":"123192052bdb389421046619f8fbf3255945a6f0","tid":2332993,"uid":34448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"墊下面貼暖包"},{"pid":"399d9ed0755ea4e8a7bb4d587d9fcc3deba62317","tid":2332993,"uid":345579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8943b95321c18f9eea8f5dc39ca233ea680d3659","tid":2332993,"uid":109629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T23:05:13.000Z","msg":"攬住佢就可以幫佢保到暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji